265
00:16:51,146 --> 00:16:52,991
would get into an accident in a place like that.

266
00:16:53,246 --> 00:16:56,995
But the police would not take me seriously.

267
00:16:56,995 --> 00:16:59,646
I suspected that something must've happened

268
00:16:59,646 --> 00:17:02,746
at the party that was held here.

269
00:17:02,746 --> 00:17:05,446
Right before the accident!

270
00:17:05,446 --> 00:17:07,646
In order to find out the truth,

271
00:17:07,646 --> 00:17:11,009
I set up wiretaps everywhere in this mansion!

272
00:17:11,009 --> 00:17:13,011
I listened to everything!

273
00:17:13,011 --> 00:17:16,346
Hirasaka who was going through a slump back

274
00:17:16,346 --> 00:17:18,346
then drowned himself in alcohol.

275
00:17:18,346 --> 00:17:21,546
That night, Hirasaka got drunk and violent again.

276
00:17:21,546 --> 00:17:25,657
Kira, who tried to calm him down was knocked down by him

277
00:17:25,657 --> 00:17:27,025
and...

278
00:17:28,279 --> 00:17:30,379
In order to hide this fact,

279
00:17:30,379 --> 00:17:33,031
Hirasaka and the others faked the accident!

280
00:17:33,031 --> 00:17:34,779
So, you took revenge.

281
00:17:34,779 --> 00:17:37,879
Yeah, I picked Sawanami to be the first

282
00:17:37,879 --> 00:17:40,379
because he was the least on his guard.

283
00:17:40,379 --> 00:17:41,779
But...

284
00:17:45,579 --> 00:17:48,579
I know everything, you know.

285
00:17:48,579 --> 00:17:50,579
Everything that you did, Mr. Mifune.

286
00:17:51,379 --> 00:17:53,679
But, don't worry.

287
00:17:53,679 --> 00:17:56,079
I won't tell anybody.

288
00:17:57,055 --> 00:18:02,479
Sawanami was saying that another woman as at the party.

289
00:18:02,479 --> 00:18:06,379
He didn't say her name, but I knew it was Shoko.

290
00:18:06,379 --> 00:18:09,379
He was trying to protect the woman he loved.

291
00:18:09,379 --> 00:18:11,979
I was actually planning to kill you first!

292
00:18:11,979 --> 00:18:15,073
Since I knew of the seance from listening to the wiretaps,

293
00:18:15,279 --> 00:18:17,075
I was going to take advantage of it!

294
00:18:17,075 --> 00:18:19,077
But, I changed my mind.

295
00:18:19,279 --> 00:18:21,079
I couldn't forgive the fact that the woman

296
00:18:21,279 --> 00:18:24,479
who was involved in Kira's death dared to blackmailed me!

297
00:18:24,479 --> 00:18:26,879
That's why I decided to kill that woman!

298
00:18:26,879 --> 00:18:28,579
You're wrong!

299
00:18:30,379 --> 00:18:32,379
You're wrong!

300
00:18:32,379 --> 00:18:36,279
I'm the one that was with Kira that day!

301
00:18:36,279 --> 00:18:37,779
Maho.

302
00:18:37,779 --> 00:18:39,097
It's a lie.

303
00:18:39,097 --> 00:18:42,879
If so, why didn't Sawanami mention your name?

304
00:18:42,879 --> 00:18:47,105
Mr. Sawanami probably didn't know my name.

305
00:18:47,105 --> 00:18:49,107
He didn't seem to be interested in a plain

306
00:18:49,279 --> 00:18:51,679
and reserved person like me.

307
00:18:51,679 --> 00:18:53,979
-No. -It's that true?

308
00:18:53,979 --> 00:18:55,579
Yes.

309
00:18:55,579 --> 00:18:59,117
That's why I thought that she was the culprit.

310
00:18:59,117 --> 00:19:02,579
Why didn't you report it to the police right away?

311
00:19:02,579 --> 00:19:07,779
I didn't want to believe that Kira was dead!

312
00:19:07,779 --> 00:19:11,129
She was what kept me living.

313
00:19:11,379 --> 00:19:13,679
I was bullied in Junior and Senior high school,

314
00:19:13,679 --> 00:19:16,279
and as an adult I used to be confined to myself.

315
00:19:16,279 --> 00:19:21,139
I owe my being able to function fairly normally to Kira.

316
00:19:21,139 --> 00:19:23,141
I encountered Kira coincidentally at a cosplay shop

317
00:19:23,141 --> 00:19:27,479
that I conjured up courage to go to for the first time.

318
00:19:27,479 --> 00:19:30,879
I guess you all think why cosplay.

319
00:19:30,879 --> 00:19:33,151
But, being able to be an inhabitant of dreamland

320
00:19:33,151 --> 00:19:35,153
for even a fleeting moment

321
00:19:35,153 --> 00:19:38,279
helped me forget the painful world of reality I lived in.

322
00:19:38,279 --> 00:19:41,879
Kira was the one who taught me that.

323
00:19:43,979 --> 00:19:47,165
I wished that everything was just a dream.

324
00:19:47,165 --> 00:19:50,279
If I reported the incident to the police and things came into light,

325
00:19:50,279 --> 00:19:53,679
I would have to accept everything as fact.

326
00:19:53,679 --> 00:19:56,679
I was afraid to do so!

327
00:19:56,679 --> 00:20:01,879
I'm sorry!

328
00:20:03,879 --> 00:20:05,183
Shoko.

329
00:20:05,379 --> 00:20:09,479
If only you didn't blackmail Mr. Mifune.

330
00:20:09,479 --> 00:20:11,189
That's wrong too.

331
00:20:11,379 --> 00:20:14,279
Shoko liked Mr. Mifune.

332
00:20:14,279 --> 00:20:15,479
What?

333
00:20:15,479 --> 00:20:18,379
Wasn't Shoko going steady with Sawanami?

334
00:20:18,379 --> 00:20:21,879
No, Shoko told me,

335
00:20:21,879 --> 00:20:25,203
"Mr. Mifune probably likes Kira"

336
00:20:25,203 --> 00:20:29,479
so she said she'd keep her feelings deep down in her heart.

337
00:20:29,479 --> 00:20:30,779
I think that Shoko

338
00:20:30,779 --> 00:20:34,979
"Mifu" -really wanted to help Mr. Mifune.

339
00:20:34,979 --> 00:20:36,379
No.

340
00:20:37,679 --> 00:20:39,217
No.

341
00:20:40,679 --> 00:20:43,579
Which means that I killed somebody

342
00:20:43,579 --> 00:20:48,479
who really wanted to protect me with my own hands?

343
00:20:48,479 --> 00:20:51,679
There was no sign of her fighting back on her body

344
00:20:51,679 --> 00:20:53,579
because when you attacked her,

345
00:20:53,579 --> 00:20:57,235
she probably felt deep grief and gave up on everything.

346
00:20:57,479 --> 00:20:59,237
That's a lie!

347
00:20:59,237 --> 00:21:02,779
A lie!

348
00:21:02,779 --> 00:21:05,243
It's a lie! A lie!

349
00:21:05,243 --> 00:21:08,979
-Hey! Cut it out! -It's a lie!

350
00:21:09,979 --> 00:21:13,251
It's a lie! A lie!

351
00:21:14,579 --> 00:21:19,257
But, why did he have to create a locked room here?

352
00:21:19,479 --> 00:21:22,079
This is just my imagination.

353
00:21:22,079 --> 00:21:25,279
Mr. Mifune, by creating a locked room

354
00:21:25,279 --> 00:21:28,579
probably wanted the police to destroy this room.

355
00:21:28,579 --> 00:21:30,679
Destroyed by the police?

356
00:21:30,679 --> 00:21:32,479
If the locked room trick is not solved,

357
00:21:32,479 --> 00:21:34,779
in order to look for a secret passage or something,

358
00:21:34,779 --> 00:21:38,079
the least they'll do is tear off the floors, right?

359
00:21:38,079 --> 00:21:41,979
And, he wanted the police to find

360
00:21:41,979 --> 00:21:46,079
Kira's body that Mr. Hirasaka and the others hid under the floor.

361
00:21:46,079 --> 00:21:47,979
He wanted the police, the very ones, who concluded

362
00:21:47,979 --> 00:21:51,279
Kira's death to be accidental to find her corpse.

363
00:21:52,879 --> 00:21:56,579
The following day, the police found Kira's body

364
00:21:56,579 --> 00:22:00,479
under the floor of the meditation room.

365
00:22:00,479 --> 00:22:04,479
Now, all the locked rooms have been opened.

