00:23:25,579 --> 00:23:26,579
"Mouri Detective Agency"

367
00:23:26,579 --> 00:23:29,079
Yatsukawa, I heard you won the Director's Award

368
00:23:29,079 --> 00:23:31,389
because of your reporting the incident!

